<div>
	<span style="float:right"><h2><%= current_user.total_score %></h2></span>
	<h2>My Score</h2>
	<P>We've changed the scoring system!</p>

	<p>There are now big bonuses for tweeting as, and spotting the real celebrities, teachers and chatbots.
	And there are penalties for just voting student on everything you see.</p>
	<p>So, think about how you tweet and vote!</p>

	<p>And: if you can find a way to game the new scoring system,
	we do have another idea up our sleeves ...</p>
</div>


<% if current_user.has_voted %>
	<hr />
	<% if current_user.school.visible %>
	<h2>Position overall in Twittest: <%= current_user.position_overall %></h2>
	<% @twittest_leaderboard.each do |user| %>
	<div>
		<span style="float:right"><%= user.position_overall %></span>
		<%= user.display_name %>
	</div>
	<% end %>
	<hr />
	<% end %>
	<% if current_user.school.visible %>
	<h2>Position in my school: <%= current_user.position_in_school %></h2>
	<% @myschool_leaderboard.each do |user| %>
	<div>
		<span style="float:right"><%= user.position_in_school %></span>
		<%= user.display_name %>
	</div>
	<% end %>
	<% end %>
	<hr />

	<% if current_user.school.visible %>
	<h2>Position of my School in Twittest: <%= current_user.school.position_overall %></h2>
	<% @school_leaderboard.each do |school| %>
	<div>
		<span style="float:right"><%= school.position_overall %></span>
		<%= school.name %>
	</div>
	<% end %>
	<% end %>
<% else %>
	<hr />
	Please vote on a tweet to view the leader-boards
<% end %>